com.jswiff.swfrecords
Class ClipEventFlags

java.lang.Object
  com.jswiff.swfrecords.ClipEventFlags
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public final class ClipEventFlags
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This class implements a container for event flags. Used in ClipActions and ClipActionRecord to indicate which events to react upon.

See Also:
ClipActions, ClipActionRecord, Serialized Form
